<p>And Charlotte Dawson dressed her blossoming bump in an oversized 'Mother' blue jumper dress as she headed out for chips in Manchester on Thursday. </p>

<p>The Ex On The Beach star, 27, headed out with Missguided's creative team, amid reports she is in the final discussions to sign a lucrative clothing deal with the brand. </p>

