<p>An insider told MailOnline: 'Charlotte's skyrocketed in popularity over lockdown and since she announced her pregnancy brands have been fighting to sign her up for an exclusive contract.</p>

<p>'Her humour makes her the perfect match for her own collection and her nearly 1 million followers on Instagram are the perfect audience to target. </p>

